snippet.title: Tribute to Video Game Music (1 Year Anniversary!)
snippet.description:
Thank you everyone for the amazing support. One year already!!
I've been uploading video game music all this time, almost daily. I hope this channel is a good tribute. I know I'm not stopping now... Here's to another year with everyone!

About this video: I wish I could have added TONS more from the list, but Youtube's 10 minutes limit hit me hard. This video only has a portion of the channel's playlist. Check it out!

2 Years Anniversary : http://www.youtube.com/watch?v=4azKyHEjEbA
3 Years Anniversary : http://www.youtube.com/watch?v=9RpdJnC2u84
4 Years Anniversary : http://www.youtube.com/watch?v=uq4ifSc7MSw
